                                                                                                                       7                                      Blues bank on Terry
                      
	London: Chelsea welcome back their defensive lynchpin and their midfield dynamo for Saturdays match against Everton as the reigning champions look to halt an alarming winless run that have cost them top spot in the EPL.         
	The return of John Terry and Michael Essien, this weekend, is set to boost Carlo Ancelottis stuttering side.         
